headline: The Trade Desk stock falls on Amazon-Roku partnership concerns
summary: Investing.com -- The Trade Desk (NASDAQ: NASDAQ:TTD) stock fell 3% Monday as investors reacted to a new partnership between Amazon (NASDAQ:AMZN) Ads and Roku (NASDAQ:ROKU) that could pose a competitive threat to the digital advertising platform.
